{"tid":1655610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實會唔會真係諗多咗？","createTime":"2019-10-15T06:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T10:52:45.000Z","uid":579,"like":5,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"cef61d2b79a47d4c4b14b913f599a7d311504991","tid":1655610,"uid":579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"可能陳彥霖真係自殺？<br />\n<br />\n1. 好早之前已經有人話佢有精神問題<br />\n睇東涌嗰條片又真係似？<br />\n<br />\n2. 佢之前同朋友提過想重新開始新生活<br />\n會唔會意思係重新做人？<br />\n<br />\n3. 佢屋企人唔想透露<br />\n係因為唔想話俾人知自己個女有精神問題所以自殺？<br />\n<br />\n4. 正常點解會赤腳喺條街度行？<br />\n可能嗰時已經有啲精神恍惚？甚至除曬衫再去跳海？<br />\n<br />\n雖然解釋唔到點解會同完朋友出街之後返完學校先去自殺<br />\n<br />\n我唔係啲風向撚 我亦相信黑警係有殺人 但可能陳同學真係唔關事？又或者會唔會有精神科醫生可以出嚟解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n其實我講咁多 <br />\n都係想大家集中返條戰線<br />\n10月20 九龍見！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ggfaTTQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FggfaTTQ.png&h=e24b0029&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ff15781fe9bcfa4dbebd817aaf4d6bff3320980","tid":1655610,"uid":150912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:04:49.000Z","msg":"咁點解要剪片呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3c6519d8575994fbe20e6a34c4c72c6cd82ddd","tid":1655610,"uid":112622,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:06:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b6de8a4f18b058258976b343a98e39398d1f3d2","tid":1655610,"uid":187116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:07:06.000Z","msg":"有諗過會唔會係黑警以外既撚樣？<br />\n襯依家社會大亂去犯事"},{"pid":"8ade48a4e80fb2895b878c66632ab4aa5d953200","tid":1655610,"uid":60023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:08:57.000Z","msg":"只想要真相"},{"pid":"bf2c5ff38c831ba0728d53079427d2548dd21e4c","tid":1655610,"uid":26687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T07:10:20.000Z","msg":"所以咪要搞清楚成件事"},{"pid":"477fa67ee2a8f389d4f16e0785ccbff3ca609704","tid":1655610,"uid":244809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s